                            <comment id="12721568" author="gsingers" created="Fri, 19 Jun 2009 00:55:55 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch that adds transpose and tests&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12721653" author="srowen" created="Fri, 19 Jun 2009 06:18:40 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Looks OK to me &amp;#8211; I applied the patch locally and tweaked a few things. Seems like a rare use case but simple to implement anyway. Mind if I submit over here?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
