                            <comment id="12722137" author="otis" created="Sat, 20 Jun 2009 05:25:16 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Really, what is the use case for this?  Wondering, since it&apos;s so easy to control the order of these 2-3 pieces of data.  Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12722171" author="gsingers" created="Sat, 20 Jun 2009 12:00:28 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;See &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.lucidimagination.com/search/document/4a2631a4adf77262/jira_commented_mahout_135_allow_filedatamodel_to_transpose_users_and_items&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://www.lucidimagination.com/search/document/4a2631a4adf77262/jira_commented_mahout_135_allow_filedatamodel_to_transpose_users_and_items&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

